---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  title={"404 - Page Not Found"}
  description={"The page you're looking for has been compromised or doesn't exist."}
	pagefindIgnore
>
  <div class="notfound-container" slot="404">
    <div class="error-code">
      <span class="error-number">4</span>
      <span class="error-icon">üîí</span>
      <span class="error-number">4</span>
    </div>
    
    <h1 class="text-glow">ACCESS DENIED</h1>
    
    <div class="error-message">
      <p>The page you're looking for has been <span class="highlight">compromised</span> or doesn't exist.</p>
      <p>Either the target has been <span class="highlight">patched</span> or you're using the wrong <span class="highlight">payload</span>.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="suggestions">
      <h3>Possible Solutions:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Check your <span class="code">URL</span> for typos</li>
        <li>Try a different <span class="code">attack vector</span></li>
        <li>Return to the <span class="code">homepage</span> and start over</li>
        <li>Check if the page has been <span class="code">moved</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="actions">
      <a class="block-link" href="/">üè† Return to Base</a>
      <a class="block-link" href="/blog">üìù Browse Blog Posts</a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="terminal-output">
      <code>$ curl -I {Astro.url.pathname}</code><br>
      <code>HTTP/1.1 404 Not Found</code><br>
      <code>X-Status: Target Not Found</code><br>
      <code>X-Suggestion: Try /blog/ instead</code>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .notfound-container {
    display: flex;
    min-height: 80vh;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    width: 100%;
    text-align: center;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 2rem;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .error-code {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    font-size: 6rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .error-number {
    color: var(--primary);
    text-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--primary);
  }

  .error-icon {
    font-size: 4rem;
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.5; }
  }

  .notfound-container h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin: 0;
    color: #ff6b6b;
  }

  .error-message {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .error-message p {
    font-size: 1.25em;
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .highlight {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .suggestions {
    background: rgba(var(--primary-rgb), 0.1);
    border: 1px solid var(--primary);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .suggestions h3 {
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .suggestions ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .suggestions li {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    padding: 0.25rem 0;
  }

  .code {
    background: rgba(var(--primary-rgb), 0.2);
    padding: 0.125rem 0.375rem;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.9em;
  }

  .actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .terminal-output {
    background: #0a0a0a;
    border: 1px solid #333;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.9em;
    color: #00ff00;
    max-width: 400px;
    text-align: left;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .terminal-output code {
    background: none;
    color: inherit;
    padding: 0;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 640px) {
    .error-code {
      font-size: 4rem;
    }
    
    .error-icon {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }
    
    .notfound-container h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    
    .actions {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
</style>